column5: Thought you may enjoy a couple of pictures of the Fish Warden I ran into during my trip to Lac Seul last month. He surely had an eagle eye as he visited me frequently during the week I was there. He was checking possession limit on the stringer every time.PJ
Looks like You "ruffled His feathers" a bit!What a MAJESTIC BIRD!I still get excited whenever I see one!
